rows.label: qst400202_msg0001
rows.name: Oh yeah, I know all about it.

rows.label: qst400202_msg0002
rows.name:
I heard some of the Imperial
guys sayin' "the execution
will be held shortly."

rows.label: qst400202_msg0003
rows.name: Those Iira people are bad news, right?

rows.label: qst400202_msg0004
rows.name:
I heard they've killed loads of
Drivers to steal their Core Crystals.

rows.label: qst400202_msg0005
rows.name:
It's amazing the Empire
managed to catch one of 'em.

rows.label: qst400202_msg0006
rows.name:
So, what do they do at an "execution"?
I've never seen one before.

rows.label: qst400202_msg0008
rows.name:
I'm definitely going to watch! You
guys shouldn't miss it either!
